c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-11_"><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-12_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-14_">Electric bikes, or ebikes, have been growing in popularity in recent years. But what exactly is an ebike, and how does it work? Letâ€™s dig througt the basics of what an ebike is, how it works, and why it's becoming a popular choice for commuters, recreational riders, and anyone looking for a fun and eco-friendly mode of transportation and also the benefit of ebikes.</span></p><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-15_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-17_">1: Definition and Types of Ebikes</span></p><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-18_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-20_">An ebike, in simple terms, is a bicycle with an electric motor and battery that assists the rider's pedaling. There are two main types of ebikes: pedal-assist and throttle-assist. Pedal-assist ebikes require the rider to pedal in order for the motor to engage and provide assistance, while throttle-assist ebikes can be powered solely by the motor without any pedaling.</span></p><div title="Definition and Types of electric bike" data-pf-type="Image" id="bg1" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-21_ pf-hide"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/t/63/assets/20221229untitled2670-1681403443513.jpg?v=1681403467" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/t/63/assets/20221229untitled2670-1681403443513.jpg?v=1681403467 1536w" width="1920" height="1020" alt="Definition and Types of electric bike" title="Definition and Types of electric bike"/></div><div title="What is an electric bike" data-pf-type="Image" id="bg1-mb" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-22_ pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/t/63/assets/20221229untitled2670-1681403443513.jpg?v=1681403467" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/t/63/assets/20221229untitled2670-1681403443513.jpg?v=1681403467 1536w" width="1920" height="1020" alt="What is an electric bike" title="What is an electric bike"/></div><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-23_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-25_">2: Components of an Ebike</span></p><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-26_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-28_">Ebikes consist of several key components that work together to provide a unique riding experience. The frame of an ebike is similar to that of a traditional bicycle but with modifications to accommodate the battery and motor. At Urtopia, we take pride in our sleek and stylish designs that blend seamlessly into any environment. Our unique frame design will make you stand out from the crowd and turn heads.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-d907" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-fmciRz bheIgq pf-29_"><div style="--cw:893px" class="sc-gjNHFA gwWIgj"><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-30_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:0px;--s-sm:15px;--s-lg:0px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gUQvok iVVDxu pf-31_"><div title="Torque sensor electric bike" data-pf-type="Image" id="bg2" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-32_ pf-hide"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/t/63/assets/20221229untitled2755-1681403443525.jpg?v=1681403474" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/t/63/assets/20221229untitled2755-1681403443525.jpg?v=1681403474 1536w" width="1920" height="1277" alt="Torque sensor electric bike" title="Torque sensor electric bike"/></div><div title="Torque sensor electric bike" data-pf-type="Image" id="bg2-mb" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-33_ pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/t/63/assets/20221229untitled2755-1681403443525.jpg?v=1681403474" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/t/63/assets/20221229untitled2755-1681403443525.jpg?v=1681403474 1536w" width="1920" height="1277" alt="Torque sensor electric bike" title="Torque sensor electric bike"/></div><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-34_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-36_">The battery provides power to the motor and can be charged using a standard outlet. The motor is usually located in the hub of the wheel or the bottom bracket and provides assistance to the rider's pedaling.&nbsp;</span></p><div title="Urtopia long range Torque sensor electric bike battery" data-pf-type="Image" id="bg3" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-37_ pf-hide"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/t/63/assets/20221229untitled2580-1681403443506.jpg?v=1681403461" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/t/63/assets/20221229untitled2580-1681403443506.jpg?v=1681403461 1536w" width="1920" height="1118" alt="Urtopia long range Torque sensor electric bike battery" title="Urtopia long range Torque sensor electric bike battery"/></div><div title="Urtopia long range Torque sensor electric bike battery" data-pf-type="Image" id="bg3-mb" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-38_ pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/t/63/assets/20221229untitled2580-1681403443506.jpg?v=1681403461" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0583/5810/4213/t/63/assets/20221229untitled2580-1681403443506.jpg?v=1681403461 1536w" width="1920" height="1118" alt="Urtopia long range Torque sensor electric bike battery" title="Urtopia long range Torque sensor electric bike battery"/></div><p class="sc-jtXEFf jydWoQ pf-39_ Body" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jKTccl dCeBIC pf-41_">The sensor determines your input and let the controller know the power that needs to output from the motor, while